     H            Y.
     F** UTLR38 ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET INVOICE#/MANIFEST# FROM AB#PP47              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2020.02.06                             *
     F*  ALLOWABLE NUNY:                                           *
     F*    0531: ISUZU                                             *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR38'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $NOHZ   8
     F*                    PARM           $NOBN   2
     F*                    PARM           $ODRN  10
     F*                    PARM           $MHIN  20
     F*                    PARM           $INVN  20
     F*                    PARM           $MANI  20
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY CODE
     F*       $NOHZ :  8A SJIP DATE
     F*       $NOBN :  2A BIN#
     F*       $ODRN : 10A PO#
     F*       $MHIN : 20A CUST PART#
     F*   OUT $INVN : 20A INVOICE#
     F*       $MANI : 20A MANIFEST#
     F*       $RTN  :  1A RETURN FLAG (BLANK=OK, *=ERROR)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PL47CIF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           KEY1      SETLLAB#PL47C
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY1      READEAB#PL47C                 98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           $INVN     IFEQ *BLANK
     C           ABRLNO    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     MOVELABRLNO    $INVN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           $MANI     IFEQ *BLANK
     C           ABMANI    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     MOVELABMANI    $MANI
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           $INVN     IFEQ *BLANK
     C           $MANI     ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *=============================================================
      *                    INITIAL PROCESS
      *=============================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $NOHZ   8
     C                     PARM           $NOBN   2
     C                     PARM           $ODRN  10
     C                     PARM           $MHIN  20
     C                     PARM           $INVN  20
     C                     PARM           $MANI  20
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K#NONY  40
     C                     KFLD           K#SHDT  80
     C                     KFLD           K#NOBN  20
     C                     KFLD           K#ODRN 10
     C                     KFLD           K#MHIN 15
      *
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     K#NONY
     C                     MOVEL$NOHZ     K#SHDT
     C                     MOVEL$NOBN     K#NOBN
     C                     MOVEL$ODRN     K#ODRN
     C                     MOVEL$MHIN     K#MHIN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $INVN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $MANI
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
